      "rationale": "A three-level mesh refinement study was performed on the pedicle screw-rod construct model. QoI changes between the medium mesh (1.2M elements) and fine mesh (3.1M elements) were 0.8% for stiffness and 1.4% for yield force. Grid Convergence Index was below 3% for all quantities, confirming discretization error is adequately controlled."
